


=IVA's=

This application lets you keep track of all IVA's that use the entity.

[ivas-listado.png]

==List of IVA's==

In the list of IVA's, you will find the most important pillars of registration:

- **Ref.:** Numeric code that identifies the VAT.
- **Name:** Name VAT.
- **Description:** Description VAT.
- **VAT rate (%):** VAT rate.


===Listing Options===

On each record. You can perform a series of actions that are represented by the following icons:

- [fa-search] [fa-pencil] [fa-trash] Check / Edit / Delete Record.


