==Form VAT==

This is the application of VAT, with it you can add, modify and view all data from the VAT classified in different tabs: main data, data on the registry modifications and assignments to folders.

===Data Tab VAT===

In this tab you can view and modify the main elements of VAT. Here we relate all information fields.

[ivas-formulario.png]

- **Name (*):** Name VAT.
- **VAT rate (%):** VAT rate.
- **Description:** Description VAT.


(*) **Required when creating or modifying a VAT Campos.**

